pyspark.sql.functions.character_length

Returns the character length of string data or number of bytes of binary data. 
The length of string data includes the trailing spaces. 
The length of binary data includes binary zeros.

Parameters
str : Column or str
        Input column or strings.

Examples

spark.range(1).select(character_length(sf.lit("SparkSQL"))).show()
+--------------------------+
|character_length(SparkSQL)|
+--------------------------+
|                         8|
+--------------------------+

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

pyspark.sql.functions.char_length

Returns the character length of string data or number of bytes of binary data. 
The length of string data includes the trailing spaces. 
The length of binary data includes binary zeros.

Parameters
str : Column or str
        Input column or strings.

Examples

spark.range(1).select(char_length(sf.lit("SparkSQL"))).show()
+---------------------+
|char_length(SparkSQL)|
+---------------------+
|                    8|
+---------------------+
